sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Frontend
    participant API as Symfony API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    User->>Frontend: Submit workspace creation form
    Frontend->>API: POST /api/workspaces { name }
    API->>API: Validate JWT and payload
    API->>DB: Insert workspace
    API->>DB: Set owner
    API->>DB: Add creator as workspace member
    DB-->>API: Workspace persisted
    API-->>Frontend: 201 Created + workspace payload
    Frontend-->>User: Refresh workspace list and select new workspace
